\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=261224\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:423:\"<p>Looking for the best SEO monitoring tools to help boost your search rankings? Keeping tabs on your performance on search engines is a crucial part of running effective SEO and digital marketing campaigns. And doing so requires a robust set&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-monitoring-tools/\">8 Best SEO Monitoring Tools for WordPress</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28323:\"<p>Looking for the best SEO monitoring tools to help boost your search rankings?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keeping tabs on your performance on search engines is a crucial part of running effective SEO and digital marketing campaigns. And doing so requires a robust set of SEO monitoring tools.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, well show you some of the best SEO monitoring tools to help you rank well in organic search.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-seo-monitoring\">What is SEO Monitoring?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-8-best-seo-monitoring-tools-for-wordpress\">8 Best SEO Monitoring Tools for WordPress</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. All In One SEO (AIOSEO)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-monsterinsights\">2. MonsterInsights</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-ahrefs\">3. Ahrefs</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-semrush\">4. Semrush</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-spyfu\">5. SpyFu</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-6-se-ranking\">6. SE Ranking</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-7-serpstat\">7. Serpstat</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-8-seobility\">8. Seobility</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-seo-monitoring-tools-your-faqs-answered\">SEO Monitoring Tools: Your FAQs Answered</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-an-seo-monitoring-tool\">What is an SEO monitoring tool?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-why-do-i-need-an-seo-monitoring-tool\">Why do I need an SEO monitoring tool?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-which-seo-monitoring-tool-is-the-best\">Which SEO monitoring tool is the best?</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-the-best-seo-monitoring-tools-for-wordpress-our-top-picks\">The Best SEO Monitoring Tools for WordPress: Our Top Picks</a></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-seo-monitoring\">What is SEO Monitoring?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO monitoring is the practice of monitoring your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-monitor-seo-performance-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Monitor SEO Performance in WordPress\">SEO performance</a> on search engines. It helps you get a clearer picture of how youre doing on search engine results pages (SERPs). For instance, youll get to know where you stand regarding:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Organic traffic</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click-through rate</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Keyword rankings</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Page speed</li>\n\n\n\n<li>And more</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>This is important information you can use to better understand whether youre meeting your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-set-seo-goals-that-boost-rankings/\" title=\"How to Set SEO Goals that Help Boost Rankings [Beginners Guide]\">SEO goals</a>. If not, SEO monitoring can also provide valuable insight into how to improve your campaigns performance and successfully hit your goals. Lets see which SEO monitoring tools can come in handy for you to succeed in your SEO goals.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-8-best-seo-monitoring-tools-for-wordpress\">8 Best SEO Monitoring Tools for WordPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Weve curated an expertly picked list of the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-tools-for-small-business/\" title=\"8 Best SEO Tools for Small Business  2024 (Free and Paid)\">best SEO tools</a> to monitor your SEO rankings. Lets dive right in, shall we?</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-1-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/\" title=\"Home\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO)</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://lh7-us.googleusercontent.com/pDLv09iO0HTvgs_TNLxoMDzp2AKtxSYRwewAK4rZTDOGFcTRKc2AbZYX8SaRbxWaRtLmOVaSpEnvtcEv8oheq3Ct10W4xFt5_w4_2J8sGqOjabW80wWifQUHDGuNjoQ1b6dvC_MOJvYWTcRZke_cGq4\" alt=\"AIOSEO is a powerful WordPress plugin that has one of the best SEO monitoring tools.\" title=\"AIOSEO is a powerful tool that can help you maintain the links on your site.\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/\" title=\"Home\">AIOSEO</a> is the best SEO monitoring tool for WordPress. Its a powerful SEO plugin boasting over 3 million active installs. Millions of savvy website owners and marketers trust the plugin to help them dominate SERPs and drive relevant site traffic. This is because the plugin has many powerful <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\" title=\"Features\">SEO features and modules</a> to help you optimize your website for search engines and users. Examples include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-cornerstone-content/\" title=\"What is Cornerstone Content? Plus Tips and Examples\">Cornerstone Content</a></strong>: Easily build topic clusters and enhance your topical authority and semantic SEO strategy.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-revisions/\" title=\"SEO Revisions\">SEO Revisions</a>:</strong> Track any changes you make to your site and see their impact on your SEO. Plus, you get to see on a timeline how Google updates affect your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/robots-editor/\" title=\"Robots.txt Editor\">Advanced Robots.txt Generator</a></strong>: Easily generate and customize your robots.txt file for better crawling and indexing.&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/truseo-score-analysis/\" title=\"TruSEO On-Page Analysis\">TruSEO Highlighter</a></strong>: Makes it easy to spot on-page SEO issues and gives recommendations for fixing them.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-aioseo-4-2-5-next-gen-schema-generator-to-improve-your-seo-rankings/\" title=\"Announcing AIOSEO 4.2.5: Next-Gen Schema Generator to Improve Your SEO Rankings\">Next-gen Schema generator</a></strong>: This no-code schema generator enables users to generate and output any schema markup on your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/redirection-manager/\" title=\"Redirection Manager\">Redirection Manager</a></strong></strong>: Helps you manage redirects and eliminate 404 errors, making it easier for search engines to crawl and index your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/internal-link-assistant/\" title=\"Link Assistant\">Link Assistant</a></strong>: Powerful internal linking tool that automates building links between pages on your site. It also gives you an audit of outbound links.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-the-seo-preview-tool/\"><strong>SEO Preview</strong></a>: This gives you an overview of your search and social snippets and general SEO so you can improve your optimization.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/indexnow/\" title=\"IndexNow\">IndexNow</a></strong>: For fast indexing on search engines that support the IndexNow protocol (like Bing and Yandex).</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/smart-xml-sitemaps/\" title=\"Smart XML Sitemaps\">Sitemap generator</a></strong>: Automatically generate different types of sitemaps to notify all search engines of any updates on your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\" title=\"Features\">And more</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most beloved features in AIOSEO is the brand-new <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/search-statistics/\" title=\"Search Statistics\">Search Statistics module</a>. This powerful Google Search Console integration lets you track your keyword rankings and see important SEO metrics with 1-click, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This powerful module makes monitoring your SEO performance easy. And you can do that right from your WordPress dashboard. To use this SEO monitoring tool, simply go to your <strong>All In One SEO</strong> menu and click on <strong>Search Statistics</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"370\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/monitor-seo-rankings-search-statistics-dashboard-new.png\" alt=\"Search Statistics dashboard.\" class=\"wp-image-187812\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/monitor-seo-rankings-search-statistics-dashboard-new.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/monitor-seo-rankings-search-statistics-dashboard-new-300x158.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/monitor-seo-rankings-search-statistics-dashboard-new-600x316.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/monitor-seo-rankings-search-statistics-dashboard-new-114x60.png 114w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/monitor-seo-rankings-search-statistics-dashboard-new-171x90.png 171w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEOs Search Statistics feature shows you many crucial SEO metrics to help you monitor your performance on search engines. Examples of said metrics include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Search impressions</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Number of clicks</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Average clickthrough rate (CTR)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Keyword rankings (including changes in positions)&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Content performance (including changes in positions)&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li>And more</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Youll get most of the information you need to get a clear picture of your SEO campaigns performance. The different reports also give you insight into what you need to do to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/search-statistics-power-hacks-to-help-boost-your-rankings/\" title=\"6 Search Statistics Power Hacks to Help Boost Your Rankings\">boost your SEO and improve your rankings</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides SEO monitoring, you can also use AIOSEO for <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-do-an-seo-competitor-analysis/\" title=\"How to Do an SEO Competitor Analysis [The Easy Way]\">competitive analysis</a>. This helps you design SEO campaigns that will give you an edge over your competitors. It also gives you a page speed analysis to ensure your technical SEO is on point.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If youre looking for the best SEO monitoring tool for WordPress, then look no further than AIOSEO. Because its an easy-to-use plugin, you dont need any coding or technical knowledge to use it to its full potential.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions on how to install AIOSEO, check out our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $49.60. A free plan (AIOSEO Lite) is also available.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-2-monsterinsights\">2. <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MonsterInsights - WordPress Analytics Plugin\" rel=\"noopener\">MonsterInsights</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"410\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-monsterinsights.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights home page\" class=\"wp-image-163394\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-monsterinsights.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-monsterinsights-300x175.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-monsterinsights-600x350.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-monsterinsights-103x60.png 103w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-monsterinsights-154x90.png 154w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MonsterInsights - WordPress Analytics Plugin\" rel=\"noopener\">MonsterInsights</a> is the best WordPress Google Analytics plugin on the market. Over 3 million users love it for its intuitive and easy-to-use interface. MonsterInsights gives you all the power of Google Analytics but with a more user-friendly interface, making it one of the best SEO monitoring tools for WordPress users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With MonsterInsights, all it takes is a single click, and youll have real-time data on your sites SEO performance. The plugin also gives you in-depth insight into the content your visitors love the most. This helps you create more of that type of content, resulting in an increase in traffic to your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>MonsterInsights also comes with different types of SEO reports based on Google Search Console (GSC) and Google Analytics (GA). Plus, it can also pull your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/yoast-vs-rank-math-vs-all-in-one-seo/\" title=\"Yoast vs Rank Math vs All in One SEO: Which Is Better?\">AIOSEO or Yoast</a> scores so you see what needs to be improved in your SEO strategy.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Real-time reporting</li>\n\n\n\n<li>SEO ranking reports</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Over 100 data points</li>\n\n\n\n<li>User behavior reports</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, if you sell digital products on your site using plugins like <a href=\"https://easydigitaldownloads.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Easy Digital Downloads - WordPress eCommerce plugin\" rel=\"noopener\">Easy Digital Downloads</a> or <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"WooCommerce\">WooCommerce</a>, MonsterInsights offers enhanced eCommerce tracking features.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These features and more make MonsterInsights one of the best SEO monitoring tools for WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at $99.50/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-3-ahrefs\">3. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Ahrefs\">Ahrefs</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"345\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-diy-seo-software-tools-ahrefs.png\" alt=\"Ahrefs home page.\" class=\"wp-image-163411\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-diy-seo-software-tools-ahrefs.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-diy-seo-software-tools-ahrefs-300x148.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-diy-seo-software-tools-ahrefs-600x296.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-diy-seo-software-tools-ahrefs-122x60.png 122w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-diy-seo-software-tools-ahrefs-183x90.png 183w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Ahrefs\">Ahrefs</a> is a comprehensive marketing and SEO toolkit to help you DIY your SEO. It also has powerful keyword research and competitor analysis tools.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once your campaigns are running, it also has some powerful SEO monitoring tools to help you keep track of your performance. This powerful tool can show you how all the pages on your website are performing on SERPs, including vital metrics like traffic, the dollar value of said traffic, and position.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also use Ahrefs for other tasks such as keyword discovery, uncovering backlink opportunities, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-track-seo-keyword-rankings-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Track SEO Keyword Rankings in WordPress\">rank tracking</a>, and more.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Data segmentation</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Shows SERP features you own</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Google Search Console (GSC) integration&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Competitor analysis</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $99.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-4-semrush\">4. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Semrush\">Semrush</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"425\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-semrush.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-163413\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-semrush.png 7