onitoring-tools-se-ranking.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/best-seo-monitoring-tools-se-ranking-300x180.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/best-seo-monitoring-tools-se-ranking-600x361.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/se-ranking/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"SE Ranking\">SE Ranking</a> is an SEO platform that can be used for several SEO-related tasks. As an SEO monitoring tool, it comes with site auditing features that help you find on-page and off-page SEO issues that could be hindering your performance.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also use the tool for keyword rank tracking and competitor analysis so you get a clear picture of where you stand in relation to your competitors. It also has a report that shows you some <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-technical-seo-the-best-checklist-in-2022/\" title=\"What Is Technical SEO? The Best Checklist in 2023\">technical SEO issues</a>. These make SE Ranking rank as one of the best SEO monitoring tools for small businesses.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Keyword rank tracker</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Website audit tools</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Competitor analysis</li>\n\n\n\n<li>SERP checker</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $31.20/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-7-serpstat\">7. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/serpstat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Serpstat\">Serpstat</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/serpstat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"370\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/best-seo-monitoring-tools-serpstat.png\" alt=\"Serpstat home page\" class=\"wp-image-261617\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/best-seo-monitoring-tools-serpstat.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/best-seo-monitoring-tools-serpstat-300x159.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/best-seo-monitoring-tools-serpstat-600x317.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/serpstat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Serpstat\">Serpstat</a> is an SEO monitoring tool designed to help marketers and small business owners dominate the SERPs by providing them with intelligent and actionable data.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This tool has an easy-to-understand dashboard that allows you to monitor your keywords and those of your competitors. Besides being a rank tracker, Serpstat also has many other SEO features like keyword research tools and an <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-on-page-seo-tools/\" title=\"Best On-Page SEO Tools for WordPress (Tested and Reviewed)\">on-page SEO analysis tool</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Rank tracker&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Site audit</li>\n\n\n\n<li>SERP crawling</li>\n\n\n\n<li>On-page SEO checker&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $69/month.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-8-seobility\">8. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/seobility/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Seobility\">Seobility</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/seobility/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"330\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/best-seo-monitoring-tools-seobility.png\" alt=\"Seobility home page\" class=\"wp-image-261619\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/best-seo-monitoring-tools-seobility.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/best-seo-monitoring-tools-seobility-300x141.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/best-seo-monitoring-tools-seobility-600x283.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/seobility/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Seobility\">Seobility</a> is an all-in-one SEO software with some pretty good SEO monitoring tools. The tool crawls your website and analyzes all your web pages. If it finds any errors, it highlights them in an easy-to-read report.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Regarding SEO monitoring, Seobility has a rank tracker that keeps you updated on the performance of your campaigns. You can also compare your competitors&#8217; SEO rankings with yours.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Google rank tracker</li>\n\n\n\n<li>SEO checker</li>\n\n\n\n<li>TF*IDF Tool (a numerical statistic used in SEO to measure the importance of a word)</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $50/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-seo-monitoring-tools-your-faqs-answered\">SEO Monitoring Tools: Your FAQs Answered</h2>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-an-seo-monitoring-tool\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What is an SEO monitoring tool?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>An SEO monitoring tool is software designed to track and analyze various aspects of a site&#8217;s performance in search engines. These tools help you monitor keyword rankings, backlinks, on-page SEO, and other metrics to improve your site&#8217;s visibility.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-why-do-i-need-an-seo-monitoring-tool\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Why do I need an SEO monitoring tool?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>SEO monitoring tools provide valuable insights into your website&#8217;s performance, allowing you to identify areas for improvement, track keyword rankings, analyze competitor strategies, and ultimately enhance your site&#8217;s search engine visibility.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-which-seo-monitoring-tool-is-the-best\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Which SEO monitoring tool is the best?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>The best SEO monitoring tool depends on individual needs and preferences. But if youre a WordPress user, All In One SEO (AIOSEO) is the best SEO monitoring tool for you. Other popular choices include Ahrefs, SEMrush, Moz, and Google Search Console (GSC).</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-the-best-seo-monitoring-tools-for-wordpress-our-top-picks\">The Best SEO Monitoring Tools for WordPress: Our Top Picks</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our top pick for the best SEO monitoring tool for WordPress is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/\" title=\"Home\">AIOSEO</a>. Its a powerful plugin that can help you improve your visibility on search engines. Plus, the Search Statistics module lets you see your search performance right from your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you find the best SEO monitoring tool for WordPress. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-start-a-small-business-blog/\" title=\"How to Start a Small Business Blog in 2023\">how to start a small business blog</a> or our list of the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-blogging-tools/\" title=\"12 Blogging Tools to Help You Grow Your WordPress Blog\">best blogging tools for WordPress</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. Youll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">X (Twitter)</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-monitoring-tools/\">8 Best SEO Monitoring Tools for WordPress</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-monitoring-tools/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"How to Optimize a Site Built with the Avada Website Builder [Using the AIOSEO Integration]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:182:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-optimize-a-site-built-with-the-avada-website-builder/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=how-to-optimize-a-site-built-with-the-avada-website-builder\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\