(678, 125, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"44833b5\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"row\",\"flex_gap\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0,\"column\":\"0\",\"row\":\"0\"},\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":96.831},\"_flex_size\":\"none\",\"_element_width\":\"initial\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"85d3802\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":48.07},\"_flex_size\":\"none\",\"_element_width\":\"initial\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3b987e4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Znate da je na\\u0161 moto \\u2013 prvo rolaj pa onda misli. A uvek popularne roll and write igre ba\\u0161 prate to, uklju\\u010duju\\u0107i i legendarni Jamb.<\\/p><p>Svojevremeno smo pri\\u010dali o igri Ganz Schon Clever, odnosno That\\u2019s So Clever! ili To Je Jako Pametno kako je glasio naziv lokalizovanog izdanja. Ova igra je formulu iz Jamba prepakovala u ne\\u0161to jo\\u0161 interesantnije i bila \\u201ckrivac\\u201d za globalnu pomamu oko igara sa kockicama.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"0a53519\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":\"50\"}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c6a37c1\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/domaciEpos\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/12\\/image_2023-12-25_010023895.png\",\"id\":40,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"4abcbc5\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"37dabd9\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>E pa, nekih godinu i kusur dana od izlaska srpskog izdanja pomenute igre, stigla je lokalizacija i njenog prvog nastavka \\u2013 Doppelt So Clever. Za sve nas koji se u nema\\u010dki jezik razumemo k\\u2019o u \\u0161panska sela, prevod je Duplo Pametnije. Opet rolate \\u0161est raznobojnih kockica, upisujete ih u \\u0161emu, ali je listi\\u0107 druga\\u010diji, pravila zakukuljena kako se \\u0161ta boduje i igra donosi neke jako zanimljive fore i fazone zbog kojih apsolutno vredi dodati je u kolekciju.<\\/p><p>A evo i kako to izgleda:<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"ef566c8\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f84a1c6\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"youtube_url\":\"https:\\/\\/youtu.be\\/NzHiHmn32nk\",\"vimeo_url\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/235215203\",\"dailymotion_url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.dailymotion.com\\/video\\/x6tqhqb\",\"videopress_url\":\"https:\\/\\/videopress.com\\/v\\/ZCAOzTNk\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"video\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"126a7b8\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"1f6ad4c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"carousel\":[{\"id\":41,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/domaciEpos\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/12\\/image_2023-12-25_010416516.png\"},{\"id\":42,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/domaciEpos\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/12\\/image_2023-12-25_010549488.png\"},{\"id\":43,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/domaciEpos\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/12\\/image_2023-12-25_010608719.png\"}],\"thumbnail_size\":\"2048x2048\",\"image_stretch\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image-carousel\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
